<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>zhǔ nǐ zuì zhī dào 迦南59</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 zhǔ nǐ zuì zhī dào wǒ men de dào lù, wǒ men de xīn sī nǐ zuì qīng chǔ.
 bù ràng wǒ píng zì jǐ, dān píng nǐ zhǐ yì, yīn wǒ zhī shì shéi qiān wǒ shǒu.
 yě xǔ yào liú hěn duō de lèi, yě xǔ yào chī hěn duō de kǔ;
 wán quán qù shùn fú, gān xīn fú shì zhǔ, zhǔ jiā lì liàng zǒu wán rén shēng lù.</lyrics>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<hymn_number>59</hymn_number>
</song>